OL,3,CSewage system needs extra #40 million
OL,4,Cfor new homes to be built
OL,6,FMore than #15 million has already been
OL,7,Fset aside for improvements, part of
OL,8,Fwhich will go towards building new
OL,9,Fstorage tanks, similar to the cavern
OL,10,Fin Snow Hill.
OL,12,FBut tens of millions of pounds are
OL,13,Fstill needed to upgrade the out-of-
OL,14,Fdate system.
OL,16,FJersey's Infrastructure Minster Andy
OL,17,FJehan has promised to work with
OL,18,Fcolleagues to ringfence extra money.
