OL,3,CSewage system needs extra #40 million
OL,4,Cfor new homes to be built
OL,6,FHe added: "We've got this funding for
OL,7,Fthis year and the next year, but we
OL,8,Fneed more funding so we can get the
OL,9,Fsewage coming here directly rather
OL,10,Fthan coming in tankers."
OL,12,FWhile the new Sewage Treatment Works
OL,13,Fat Bellozanne can deal with waste for
OL,14,Fup to 140,000 people, the pipes
OL,15,Fstretching out across the island need
OL,16,Fimproving.
OL,18,FHead of Liquid Waste Duncan Berry has
OL,19,Fsaid it is "a big issue".
