OL,3,CSewage system needs extra #40 million
OL,4,Cfor new homes to be built
OL,6,FHe added: "Much of our network is at
OL,7,Fcapacity so if we now allow more
OL,8,Fhouses to connect we'll end up
OL,9,Fspilling and causing pollution so we
OL,10,Fneed to upgrade the network before we
OL,11,Fcan allow future development."
OL,13,FAt the time of the scrutiny review,
OL,14,FDeputy Steve Ahier agreed that major
OL,15,Fimprovements are needed.
OL,17,FHe explained: "I'd like to reassure
OL,18,Fislanders that this is a priority.
